title: BRIEF-Venher Invest lowers stake in Fly.pl to 1.68 pct
text:
BRIEF-Venher Invest lowers stake in Fly.pl to 1.68 pct 
Oct 12 Fly.pl SA : 
* Venher Invest Sp. z o.o. reduces stake in the company to 1.68 percent from 5.22 percent via a sale of 1,470,000 shares (or 3.54 percent stake) Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
